# C++ LLM Application
#
# The C++ LLM app is built as part of the C++ runtime (runtimes/cpp/).
# The entry point is runtimes/cpp/runtime.cpp which contains the
# prompt->generate loop, streaming output, and profiling.
#
# Build:
#   cd gitignore/runtimes/cpp/build
#   cmake ../../../../runtimes/cpp
#   cmake --build . --config Release
#
# Run:
#   ./Release/backpack_runtime --model path/to/model.gguf --prompt "Hello"
#   ./Release/backpack_runtime --model path/to/model.gguf --max-tokens 100
#   ./Release/backpack_runtime --model path/to/model.gguf --profile
